Place ONNX model files here.

Expected files:
  - backbone_fp32.onnx   (required for production inference, CLIP ViT-B/32 → 256-dim)
  - backbone_fp16.engine  (optional TensorRT FP16 engine for GPU acceleration)

Without these files, set IMGSRCH_ALLOW_MOCK_INFERENCE=true for dev/testing.
The Dockerfile copies this directory into the image at /models/.
